<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sv">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Nyheter & announcements — Joakim Jaksen</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
  <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>📣</text></svg>" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
  <style>
    .ny-wrap { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.25rem; }
    .ny-header { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
    .ny-header h1 { color: #f1f5f9; margin: 0 0 0.4rem; font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .ny-header p  { color: #94a3b8; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    .ny-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }

    .ny-card {
      display: block;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e293b, #0f172a);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .ny-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.4);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .ny-meta {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
      font-size: 0.75rem; color: #94a3b8;
    }
    .ny-date {
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      color: #64748b;
    }
    .ny-segment {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.15);
      color: #a5b4fc;
      border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.25);
    }
    .ny-segment-premium { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.15);  color: #4ade80; border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.25); }
    .ny-segment-pro     { background: rgba(251,191,36,0.15); color: #fbbf24; border-color: rgba(251,191,36,0.25); }
    .ny-segment-paid    { background: rgba(251,191,36,0.12); color: #fbbf24; border-color: rgba(251,191,36,0.25); }
    .ny-segment-free    { background: rgba(100,116,139,0.15); color: #94a3b8; border-color: rgba(100,116,139,0.25); }

    .ny-subject {
      color: #f1f5f9;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
    }
    .ny-preview {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 0;
      display: -webkit-box;
      -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
      -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .ny-arrow { float: right; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.2rem; }

    .ny-empty {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
      color: #64748b;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .ny-empty-icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="block-page">

  <a href="#main-content" class="skip-to-main">Hoppa till innehåll</a>

  <nav class="learn-nav">
    <a href="/dashboard" class="learn-nav-back">← Dashboard</a>
    <span class="learn-nav-title">📣 Nyheter</span>
    <span class="learn-nav-user"><%= username %></span>
  </nav>

  <main id="main-content" class="ny-wrap">

    <div class="ny-header">
      <h1>📣 Nyheter & announcements</h1>
      <p>Alla meddelanden från Joakim samlade på ett ställe. Missa ingenting — även om mejlet hamnar i skräpposten.</p>
    </div>

    <% if (!broadcasts || !broadcasts.length) { %>
      <div class="ny-empty">
        <div class="ny-empty-icon">📭</div>
        <p>Inga announcements än.<br>När Joakim släpper något nytt dyker det upp här.</p>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <div class="ny-list">
        <% broadcasts.forEach(function(b) {
          const dt = new Date(b.sent_at);
          const dateStr = dt.toLocaleDateString('sv-SE', { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric' });
          // Kort preview (strippa HTML + trunca)
          const preview = (b.body || '').replace(/<[^>]*>/g, ' ').replace(/\s+/g, ' ').trim().slice(0, 200);
          // Segment-label
          const segLabel = b.segment === 'premium' ? '✓ Premium' :
                           b.segment === 'pro'     ? '⚡ Pro'     :
                           b.segment === 'paid'    ? '⭐ Betalande' :
                           b.segment === 'free'    ? 'Gratis' :
                           'Alla';
        %>
          <a href="/nyheter/<%= b.id %>" class="ny-card">
            <span class="ny-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            <div class="ny-meta">
              <span class="ny-date"><%= dateStr %></span>
              <span class="ny-segment ny-segment-<%= b.segment %>"><%= segLabel %></span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="ny-subject"><%= b.subject %></h2>
            <p class="ny-preview"><%= preview %></p>
          </a>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
    <% } %>

  </main>

  <script src="/heartbeat.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
